high_descs: Turn left and walk to the toilet.
Take the soap off the top of the toilet tank.
Take a few steps left to the left sink.
Wash the soap in the sink.
Turn right and walk to the far side of the toilet.
Place the soap on the toilet tank in front of the soap bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap on a toilet tank.

high_descs: walk over to the left side of the toilet
take the soap form the back of the toilet
rinse the soap in the sink and take back out
walk to the right side of the toilet
put the soap back on the back of the toilet
anns.task_desc: get the soap from the back of the toilet, rinse it in the sink, then return it to its spot on the toilet

high_descs: Pick up the bar of soap on top of the toilet
Wash the bar of soap in the sink
Place the bar of soap on top of the toilet
